thread.title: Rangers take lead on bizarre play in Game 5 of ALDS

title: Rangers take lead on bizarre play in Game 5 of ALDS
text:
> Texas Rangers take lead on bizarre play in Game 5 of ALDS Texas Rangers' Rougned Odor celebrates with teammates after scoring on an error Toronto Blue Jays catcher Russell Martin (not shown) during the seventh inning in Game 5 of baseball's American League Division Series, Wednesday, Oct. 14, 2015 in Toronto.
